      </prodinfo>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>  <context>
    <p>Follow these guidelines to enter characters for passwords and other settings.</p><p>
      <fig>
        <image href="../media/image59.jpeg"/>
      </fig>
    </p><ul id="ul_10513306">
      <li>To scroll through the characters, press the arrow buttons.</li>
      <li>To make a selection, press the <b>OK</b>button.</li>
      <li>To change the character case or type, select <b>A1#</b>or press the <fig>
          <image href="../media/image60.png"/>
        </fig> reset button.</li>
      <li>To move the cursor to the left or right, select <fig>
          <image href="../media/image61.png"/>
        </fig> or <fig>
          <image href="../media/image62.png"/>
        </fig> .</li>
      <li>To add a space, select <fig>
          <image href="../media/image63.png"/>
        </fig>.</li>
      <li>To delete the previous character, select <fig>
          <image href="../media/image64.png"/>
        </fig>.</li>
    </ul>
  </context></taskbody>
</task>
